378
00:47:57,811 --> 00:48:00,834
- Aw, you come here often?
- I don't even drink!

379
00:48:00,835 --> 00:48:05,065
That's obvious.  You're not still
upset about this afternoon, are you?

380
00:48:05,066 --> 00:48:07,053
That isn't half of it ...

381
00:48:07,055 --> 00:48:09,954
I'm so messed up
about a lot of things.

382
00:48:09,956 --> 00:48:15,305
And now this girl I have met ...
I don't know what's going on anymore.

383
00:48:17,056 --> 00:48:19,517
Tell you what.
Why don't you and that ...

384
00:48:19,521 --> 00:48:22,531
